{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"“Comiket 92”, Ajang Bertemunya Para Cosplayer Jepang","content":"<p>Bro sis suka melihat Cosplayer? Atau malah suka Cosplay? Nah, mungkin bro sis bakal tertarik sama acara satu ini. <strong>Comic Market</strong> atau yang lebih dikenal dengan istilah “<em>Comiket” </em> ini adalah pameran dan pasar <strong><em>dojinshi</em></strong>  terbesar di dunia yang diadakan setahun dua kali. Biasanya di bulan Agustus dan Desember di Tokyo, Jepang.</p>\n<p>Acara yang dilangsungkan selama 2 – 3 hari ini diadakan di gedung Tokyo Big Sight. Itu loh gedung yang biasanya menjadi pusat pameran internasional Tokyo. Dan kabarnya acara ini dikunjungi sampai setengah juta pengunjung. Wah, keren banget ya bro sis!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13936\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13936\" data-attachment-id=\"13936\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/1-126/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tokyo Big Sight, Ariake, Tokyo (businesseventstokyo.org)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tokyo Big Sight, Ariake, Tokyo (businesseventstokyo.org)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-21.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-21.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13936\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-21.jpg\" alt=\"Tokyo Big Sight, Ariake, Tokyo (businesseventstokyo.org)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13936\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tokyo Big Sight, Ariake, Tokyo (businesseventstokyo.org)</p></div></p>\n<p>Buat yang belum tau apa itu <em>dojinshi, dojinshi</em> diambil dari kata <em>doujin</em> yaitu manga buatan para fans atau komik manga buatan orang – orang yang belum berhasil menjadi mangaka professional (orang yang karyanya sudah berhasil diterima dan diterbitkan oleh perusahaan penerbit manga).</p>\n<p><em>Dojinshi</em> ini biasanya dibuat dari manga – manga populer yang dibuatkan kembali ceritanya oleh para fans sesuai imajinasi dari fans. Misalnya manga Naruto, nah <em>dojinshi</em>-nya itu cerita tentang tokoh Naruto dan Sakura menikah. Padahal di manga aslinya, Naruto menikah dengan Hinata.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13939\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13939\" data-attachment-id=\"13939\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/6-77/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13939\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-15.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13939\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sedikit info buat bro sis, dojinshi ini biasanya terkenal dengan kategori “dewasa”. Memang di negeri asal manga alias Jepang, manga kategori dewasa cukup banyak diminati. Jadi gak heran kalau yang diketahui oleh orang – orang (diluar Jepang) hanya anggapan kalau <em>dojinshi </em>= manga dewasa<em>.</em> Padahal gak semua dojinshi adalah dewasa, ada banyak dojinshi yang dibuat tanpa konten – konten dewasa.</p>\n<p>Pameran yang pertama kali diselenggarakan di tahun 1975 ini diiisi dengan penjualan hasil karya mulai dari dojinshi, anime, <em>video games, </em>kostum untuk <em>cosplay, action figure </em>hingga aksesori. Diselenggarakan oleh “<em>Comic Market Setsuei-bu</em>”, pameran ini bertujuaan untuk berkomunikasi dengan sesama penggemar dan bukan untuk mencari keuntungan penjualan secara besar.</p>\n<p>Daya tarik <em>Comiket</em> lumayan bagus loh! Selain dari <em>dojinshi</em> yang dijual ada juga cosplay. Nah, uniknya untuk menjual <em>dojinshi</em>, si pembuat rela untuk cosplay menjadi karakter yang sama dengan <em>dojinshi</em> di area <em>Comiket</em>.</p>\n<p>Sebuah usaha yang bagus untuk mempromosikan karya, ya hehehe. Gak hanya jadi ajang promosi tapi juga menunjukkan kreativitas dan ajang silaturahmi bagi para <em>cosplayer</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13941\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13941\" data-attachment-id=\"13941\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/8-47/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplay Naruto (www.anime-now.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplay Naruto (www.anime-now.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13941\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-8.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplay Naruto (www.anime-now.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13941\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplay Naruto (www.anime-now.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13940\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13940\" data-attachment-id=\"13940\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/7-60/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplay “One Piece” (www.anime-now.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplay “One Piece” (www.anime-now.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13940\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-12.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplay “One Piece” (www.anime-now.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13940\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplay “One Piece” (www.anime-now.com)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13938\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13938\" data-attachment-id=\"13938\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/5-98/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-16.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-16.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13938\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-16.jpg\" alt=\"Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13938\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cosplay Promosi Dojinshi (jurnalotaku.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Walaupun kelihatan meriah, tapi tahun ini ada yang aneh loh dengan <em>Comiket</em>. Laporan pengunjung <em>Comiket 92</em> adalah 500.000 orang, memang bukan jumlah yang sedikit ya bro sis. Tapi ternyata angka ini mengalami penurunan, tahun kemarin, <em>Comiket 90</em> berhasil mencapai total 530.000 pengunjung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_13942\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-13942\" data-attachment-id=\"13942\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/comiket-92-ajang-bertemunya-para-cosplayer-jepang/attachment/9-39/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kerumunan Antrian masuk Comiket (Pacificcross-cultural.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kerumunan Antrian masuk Comiket (Pacificcross-cultural.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-13942\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-7.jpg\" alt=\"Kerumunan Antrian masuk Comiket (Pacificcross-cultural.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-13942\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kerumunan Antrian masuk Comiket (Pacificcross-cultural.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Usut punya usut, katanya sih suhu yang terlalu panas di acara sampai adanya <em>dojinshi</em> di pasar lokal membuat masyarakat menjadi malas untuk datang. Sebuah ironi bagi acara <em>dojinshi</em> kreatif paling besar di dunia.</p>\n<p>Ya, walaupun begitu peminatnya masih banyak ya. Kira – kira bro sis ada yang tertarik untuk datang di akhir tahun?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"10e6e6fb-4bda-5083-ad59-62537056343c"}}}